{"tid":2188084,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"小花話唔走了","createTime":"2020-09-04T04:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T11:10:26.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b07589e3065187ec8aa9cb5a709b0c321e5b5599","tid":2188084,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/09/04/e/e51d0a8832848927a9fafb9121a32d7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F09%2F04%2Fe%2Fe51d0a8832848927a9fafb9121a32d7f.jpg&h=e28b57d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  美斯（Lionel Messi）的決心動搖了，在父親的周旋之下，美斯正在重新考慮留隊的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n  當地時間週三早上，美斯父親豪爾赫（Jorge Messi）乘機抵達巴塞隆拿，在與律師見面後又同巴塞主席貝圖美奧（Josep Bartomeu）進行了一個多小時的會面。不過根據西媒的消息，這次會面雙方沒有達成一致，而談話的氛圍很融洽。<br />\n<br />\n  週四，美斯父親又來到美斯的住處與美斯見面談了一個小時，雖然目前各方都沒有採取進一步的行動，但西班牙媒體表示，美斯正在重新考慮。<br />\n<br />\n  《每日體育報》打出「他正在考慮」的標題。表示美斯在研究留下的可能性，貝圖美奧的堅定立場讓美斯很難自由離開。也許他會在巴塞履行完最後一年的合約，明夏再以自由身離開巴塞。"},{"pid":"92234718b40ab93ce8a4d45cfd61db558ae5cabb","tid":2188084,"uid":36906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:38:45.000Z","msg":"食屎啦"},{"pid":"a55ccf2b7a09b5ff5dbf1cf7a7417d66508fe3ab","tid":2188084,"uid":233327,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:39:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd911501383ca48db7144fef315cbd7b4af0190f","tid":2188084,"uid":80647,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:39:20.000Z","msg":"都估到啦，次次輸波都係彈出彈入"},{"pid":"8c0da1f3b1309f42ec19c524d3b0161e502aa49e","tid":2188084,"uid":25345,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"fd911501383ca48db7144fef315cbd7b4af0190f","tid":2188084,"uid":80647,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:39:20.000Z","msg":"都估到啦，次次輸波都係彈出彈入"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:39:49.000Z","msg":"球壇方唐鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.g